title: JLL Income Property Trust Announces Q2 2015 Earnings Call
text:
JLL Income Property Trust Announces Q2 2015 Earnings Call JLL Income Property Trust 7 hours ago ÓÅ± Done 
CHICAGO, IL--(Marketwired - Aug 7, 2015) - JLL Income Property Trust, an institutionally-managed, non-listed, daily valued perpetual life REIT ( NASDAQ : ZIPIMX ), will hold a public earnings call on Thursday, August 13, 2015 at 10:00 a.m. CDT to review second quarter 2015 operating and financial results. Allan Swaringen, Chief Executive Officer of JLL Income Property Trust, and Gregg Falk, Chief Financial Officer will present an overview of recent economic events that directly influence the business of the Company and commercial real estate markets, along with a detailed review of the financial performance and more noteworthy accomplishments of the quarter. 
Date: Thursday, August 13 Dial-in Number (Toll Free): 877-407-9205 Dial-in Number (International): 201-689-8054 
Replay Number (Toll Free): 1-877-660-6853 Replay Number (International): 1-201-612-7415 Conference ID #: 13604323 Teleconference Replay Available Until: 8/20/2015 at 10:59 PM CDT The audio replay will be posted to the Investor Relations section of the JLL Income Property Trust website at www.jllipt.com within 24 hours of the call. 
JLL Income Property Trust is a non-listed, daily valued perpetual life real estate investment trust (REIT) that gives investors access to a growing portfolio of commercial real estate investments selected by an institutional investment management team and sponsored by one of the world's leading real estate services firms. 
For more information on JLL Income Property Trust, please visit our website at www.jllipt.com .
